premise_source_doc_sentence: The Tyra Banks Show , also known as and shortened to Tyra or The Tyra Show , is an American talk show hosted by Tyra Banks .
Cycle 13 's Ashley Howard was also scouted at The Tyra Banks Show , while Cycle 15 contestants Jane Randall and Kendal Brown were scouted through a photo challenge on Tyra Banks ' website .
Hrvatski Top Model  (  Croatia 's Top Model  )  is a Croatian reality television series based on Tyra Banks ' America 's Next Top Model and is aired on RTL .
Srpski Top Model  (  Serbia 's Top Model  )  was a Serbian reality documentary television show based on Tyra Banks ' America 's Next Top Model , and was aired on Prva .
Top Model po-russki , cycle 1 was the first installment of the Russian adaptation of Tyra Banks ' America 's Next Top Model .
